HEADWORD: Brutalize
<hw>Bru"tal*ize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Brutalized</conjf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. &
vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Brutalizing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>brutaliser</ets>.]</ety> <def>To make brutal; beasty; unfeeling; or
