==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Brutalize
<hw>Bru"tal*ize</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To become brutal, inhuman,
barbarous, or coarse and beasty.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He mixed . . . with his countrymen, <qex>brutalized</qex> with
them in their habits and manners.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brutally</ent>⟦br⟧
